The following officials were present: 

Colonel Nicolas Urcullu, Spanish Army, representing the
                                        Spanish Embassy;

Mr. Thomas Hinckley, representing the Department of
                                        State;

Admiral Knight, U. S. N., representing the Navy
                                        Department;

Commander Luis Suanzes, and officers of the Almirante Lobo;


The Commandant, and officers of Portsmouth, N. H. Navy
                                        Yard;

Captain Wallace and Aid, from Fort Constitution.
